UnitPriceGuard::setTwapAdapter
├── when called by owner
│   └── it stores the adapter for the LP token
└── when called by a non-owner
    └── it reverts


UnitPriceGuard::checkPrice
├── when adapter is missing
│   └── it reverts
├── when TWAP is zero
│   └── it reverts
├── when deviation is below threshold
│   └── it returns true
├── when deviation equals threshold
│   └── it reverts
└── when deviation is above threshold
    └── it reverts
